<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	《无能子》的思想及其资料来源（一）
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">全根先</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《无能子》是晚唐无名氏所撰的一本哲学著作。《唐书&middot;艺文志&middot;道家类》载有《无能子》三卷，并云:&ldquo;不著撰人名氏，光启中，隐民间&rdquo;，《四库全书总目提要》作者因其序中有&ldquo;不述其姓名游宦&rdquo;一语，疑其&ldquo;尝登仕籍，非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">隐</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">民也&rdquo;。则无能子前曾作吏，后因不得志或</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">感</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">于时伤、退而过隐居生活也未可知。又据本书中《答通问篇》说:&ldquo;无能子贫，其昆弟之子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">且</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">寒且饥，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">嗟</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">吟者相从焉，&rdquo;可见其家境清寒，显非达官显贵。而其友人序中说他&ldquo;民舍之</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">陋</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">，杂处其间，循循如也&rdquo;。</span><span>1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">从其思想境界看，无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">的隐居，许不是为了沽名钓誉，走&lsquo;终南捷径&rdquo;，很可能是出于对当时社会现实的深刻不满，而走上隐居自安这条道路。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">从序中可知，《无能子》原为三十四篇，分</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">、中、下三卷。1981年中华书局出版了王明根据明代正统《道藏》本所作的校注本，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">这</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">实际</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">上</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">也是迄今为止最早的一个《无能子》</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">校</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">注本，由此也可以想见以往学者对《无能子》的研究之少。据王明说，今存的《无能子》，只有《道藏》本有其完整篇目，其他都目录不全。该书还附有历代目录学家对于《无</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子》一书的著录，共十一家，而其中比较值得注意的是宋</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">晁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">公武的《郡斋读书后志》与清</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">四库全书总</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">目</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">提要》的说法。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">晁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">公武提出无能子&ldquo;成书三十篇&rdquo;，而《四库提要》作者说其所见为三十四篇，如果加上缺篇，共有四十二篇，并进而怀疑原书所序已经后人篡改。今按王明校注本，现存共二十三篇，若加上某些篇中所含小篇，则为三十四篇，再加上缺篇数，则为四十二篇，不知《四库提要》作者是否据此而得四十二篇，也不知</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">晁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">说有何依据?未可定论。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">关于《无能子》一书的思想倾向，历代学者都已指出，即&ldquo;述老庄自然之旨。&rdquo;以老庄自然无为的思想为其基本观点，反对儒家所提倡的封建正统思想，而以整个封建礼教为其批判对象，则是它的中心内容。因而这本书在其资料取舍上，多采用老庄的思想，同时参以《列子》、佛学及玄学的一些观点</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">在某些地方，也采纳或基本接受了法家及儒家的一些主张。大体说来，《无能子》引用前人思想成果，可以归纳为三种形式，或直接引用，或略加变化，或暗用别家思想而以自己的语言表达，而以最后一种为多。为叙述方便起见，本文在探究《无能子》的思想倾向及其资料来源时，仍以不同的思想流派为论述的分段标准</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">一、《无能子》引用老庄思想</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">老庄思想是无能子思想的主旨。可以说，在无能子思想的一些基本方面，他都采用了老庄的思想，尤其是自然无为的主张。下面，分几个方面加以论述。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">(一)论自然之始</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《无能子&middot;圣过篇》说:&ldquo;天地未分，混沌一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">炁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">炁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">充溢，分为二仪。有清浊焉，有轻重焉。轻清者上，为阳为天</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">重浊者</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">下</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">，为阴为地矣。天则刚健而动，地则柔顺而静，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">炁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">之自然也。天地既位，阴阳</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">炁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">交，于是裸虫、鳞虫、毛虫、羽虫、甲虫生焉。&rdquo;按这里所说的由</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;一炁</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;而&ldquo;分为二仪&rdquo;，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">天地阴阳，再生就裸虫、鳞虫、毛虫、羽虫、甲虫等天地万物的思想，实际上是老子思想的继承和发展。《老子》第四十二章说:&ldquo;道生一，一生二，二生三，三生万物。万物负阴而抱阳，冲气以为和。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">老子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">有时称&ldquo;道&rdquo;为&ldquo;一&rdquo;，所谓</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">道生一，&rdquo;即&ldquo;道&rdquo;自本自根，自生自成</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;一生二&rdquo;即&ldquo;道&rdquo;分为阴阳二气</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">阴阳二气的统一叫做&ldquo;冲气&rdquo;(冲虚之气)，由阴气、阳气、冲气</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">三</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">者产生万物，所以都包含阴阳的对立，而在冲虚之中得到统一。《老子》关于&ldquo;道&rdquo;的思想对后世影响极大，《无能子》受其影响不足为怪。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">(二)论&ldquo;礼&rdquo;、&ldquo;法&rdquo;、道德之起源</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《无能子》说:&ldquo;太古时，裸虫与鳞毛羽甲杂处，雌雄</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">牝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">牡，自然相合，无男女夫妇之别，父子兄弟之序。&rdquo;只是到了后来，&ldquo;裸虫中繁其智虑者，其名</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">人，以法限鳞毛羽甲诸虫&rdquo;，并&ldquo;设婚嫁以析雌雄</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">牝</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">牡，于是有夫妇之别，父子兄弟之序&rdquo;。&ldquo;又于其中择一以统众，名一为君，名众为臣。一可役众，众不得凌一。于是有君臣之分，尊卑之节。&rdquo;&ldquo;既而贱慕贵，贫慕富，而人之争心生焉&rdquo;。&ldquo;于是立仁义忠信之教，礼乐之章以拘之&rdquo;。&ldquo;降及后代，嗜欲愈炽，于是背仁义忠信，逾礼乐而争焉。谓之圣人者悔之，不得已乃设刑法</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">与兵</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">以制之，小则刑之，大则兵之&rdquo;。而&ldquo;生民困贫，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">夭</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">折之苦，漫漫不止。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span>2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">即在无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">看来，君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">臣</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">尊卑，仁义忠信，礼乐之章，皆非自然而有，而是&ldquo;圣人&rdquo;的&ldquo;强名&rdquo;，是历史发展的产物，且有害无益。按这一观点，显然与老庄思想颇为契合</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《老子》十八章说:&ldquo;大道废，有仁义</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">智慧出，有大伪。&rdquo;三</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">十</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">八章:</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">失道而后德，失德而后仁，失仁而后义，失义而后礼。&rdquo;&ldquo;礼者忠信之薄，而乱之首。&rdquo;又说:&ldquo;天下多忌讳，而民弥贫</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">民多利器，国家滋昏</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">人多伎巧，奇物滋起</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">法令滋章，盗贼多有</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。&rdquo;</span><span>3</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;绝圣弃智，民利百倍。&rdquo;</span><span>4</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">《庄子&middot;马蹄篇》也说:&ldquo;夫至德之世，同与禽兽居，族与万物并，恶乎知君</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">小人哉?&rdquo;&ldquo;圣人不死，大盗不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">止；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">绝圣弃智，大盗</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">乃止。&rdquo;</span><span>5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">(三)&ldquo;无为&rdquo;思想</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;无为&rdquo;思想是无能子思想的一个重要方面，也可以说是他立身处世的基本法则和理想要求。在《无能子》一书中，可以看到许多关于&ldquo;无为&rdquo;思想的论述。如《明本篇》说:&ldquo;夫所谓本者，无为之为心也，形骸依之以</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">立</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">也，其为常而不殆也。&rdquo;在无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">看来，&ldquo;无为&rdquo;是一切的根本，是自然的法则，甚至&ldquo;有为&rdquo;的目的也全在于&ldquo;无为&rdquo;。在《文王说篇》中，他还借用西伯的话阐发了这一思想</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;西伯</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">:夫无为之德，包裹天地</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">有为之德，开物成事。&rdquo;&ldquo;天地无为也，日月星辰，运乎</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">昼</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">夜，雨露霜雪，零</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">秋冬，江河流而不息，草木生而不</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">止，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">故无为则能无滞。若滞</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">有为，则不能无为矣。&rdquo;&ldquo;无为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">是根本，&ldquo;有为&rdquo;的目是为了&ldquo;无为&rdquo;，为&ldquo;无为&rdquo;之阶段，这实际上暗含着对&ldquo;无为而无不为&rdquo;思想的认识。《无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">》中认为，&ldquo;无为&rdquo;，&ldquo;无心&rdquo;，一任自然，无住而不适，可以立于不败之地，这也正是老庄思想中的一个</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">重</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">要方面。《老</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">》说:&ldquo;道常无为而无不为。&rdquo;</span><span>6</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;无为&rdquo;即是自然，&ldquo;生而不有，为而不恃，长而不宰。&rdquo;</span><span>7</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">道&rdquo;是自然地生成万物，而不据为己有，也不为之主宰。又说:&ldquo;人法地，地法天，天法道，道法自然。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span>8</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">人如何效法天地自然?也不过是&ldquo;以辅万物之自然而不敢为。&rdquo;</span><span>9</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">又庄子也力主&ldquo;无为&rdquo;，谓&ldquo;无以人灭天，无以故灭命，无以得殉命</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。&rdquo;</span><span>10</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">一</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">种彻底的否定人道原则的立场。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">(四)</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">超越是非思想</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">与&ldquo;无为&rdquo;思想相应的，超越是非思想也是无能子思想的一个重要方面。对此，无能子也有不少论述。他说:&ldquo;夫君子寄形以处世，虚心以应物，无邪无正，无是无</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">，无善无恶，无功无罪。虚乎心，虽尧舜夔契，非功也。则大夫之忠信，靳尚之邪楼，孰分其是非邪?无所分别，则忠信邪按一也。有所分，则分者自妄也。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">在他看来，所谓是非善恶这些观念，完全是人的&ldquo;自妄&rdquo;的行为，如果&ldquo;虚心以应物，&rdquo;则全无分别。因而他又说:&ldquo;妄为君臣之中，妄殷有称。妄殷之中，妄辛有称。妄辛之中，妄暴妄虐，以充妄欲。姬发之动，亦欲也。欲则妄，所谓以妄取妄者也。夫无为则淳正而当天理，父</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">君臣何有哉?有为则嗜欲而乱人性，孝不孝忠不忠何异哉</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">？&rdquo;</span><span>12</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">在《孙登说篇》中，他更</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">用</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">孙登的话来批评</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">嵇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">康，以阐述自己的思想:&ldquo;吾闻诸老聘</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">曰</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">:&lsquo;良贾深藏若虚，君子盛德容貌若愚。&rsquo;吾尝得汝《贻山巨源绝交书》，其问</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">二</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">大不可七不堪，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">皆</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">矜己疵物之说，时之所</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">增也。夫虚其中者，朝市不喧</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">；欲其中</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">者，岩谷不幽。仕不能夺汝之情，处不能济汝之和。仕则累，不仕则已。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">而</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">又绝人之交，增以矜己疵物之说，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">啅</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">噪于尘世之中，而欲操乎永生，可谓恶影而走乎日中者也。何足闻吾之</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">诲</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">哉?&rdquo;他认为</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">嵇</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">康因沉溺</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">是非，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">与由巨源</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">绝交，招人非议，终致</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">遭杀身之祸，实在不足称道</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">按超越是非的思想，庄子表达得最为突出。《庄子&middot;齐物沦》说:&ldquo;仁义之端，是非之途，樊然混淆，吾恶能知其辩?&rdquo;&ldquo;未成乎心，而有是非，是今</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">日</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">适越而昔至也，是以无有为有&rdquo;，又说:&ldquo;不谴是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">，以与世俗处&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">。</span><span>13</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">兹不赘述。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">(五)破&ldquo;美名&rdquo;、&ldquo;富贵&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">从&ldquo;无为&rdquo;的观点出发，无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">对于世人所追逐的富贵与美名也是有异议的。他说:&ldquo;天</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">下</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">人所共趋之而不知</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">止</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">者，富贵</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">与</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">美名尔。所谓富贵者，是</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">物尔。&rdquo;&ldquo;夫物者，人之所能为者也，自为之，反为不为者感之，乃以足物者为富贵，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">无</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">物者为贫贱，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">是乐富贵，耻贫贱，不得其乐者，无所不至，自</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">古</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">及今，醒而不悟。&rdquo;。</span><span>14</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">在他</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">看</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">来，所谓富贵，无</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">非</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">是足</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">於</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">物，而物是人自己所能制造的，自己劳动所创造的，反而被不劳动的人所获得，又进而以富贵为荣，以贫贱为耻，追逐不休，实在是误人歧途。又说:&ldquo;夫所谓美名者，岂不以居家孝、事上忠、朋友信、临财廉、充乎才、足乎艺之类耶?此皆所谓圣人者尚之，以拘愚人也。&rdquo;不难看出，无能子这些轻视名利，以富贵美名为圣人所&ldquo;强名&rdquo;以&ldquo;诱愚人&rdquo;的思想，也同样渊源于老庄。《老子》说:&ldquo;名与身孰亲?身与货孰多?</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span>15</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;见素抱朴，少私而寡欲。&rdquo;</span><span>16</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;五色令人目盲，&hellip;&hellip;驰骋败猎令人心狂，难得之货使人行妨，&rdquo;</span><span>17</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;是以圣人欲不欲，而不贵难得之货。&rdquo;</span><span>18</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">叫人淡泊名利，不要使这些身外之物来妨碍自己的身心。庄子也说:&ldquo;以道观之，物无贵贱。以物观之，自贵而相贱。以俗观之，贵贱不在己。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&rdquo;</span><span>19</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">由此可知无能子之思想乃继承老庄而略加阐发。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">在《无能子》一书中，还可以见到不少无能</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">子</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">继承和发挥老庄思想的地方，如其关于</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">&ldquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’">柔弱胜刚强&rdquo;、&ldquo;功成身退&rdquo;以及庄子所谓&ldquo;处乎材与不材之间&rdquo;等论述。这里不再详举。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: ’yes’"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<!--EndFragment-->
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
